(Cityscape, Palm Latitudes, Dec. 5) was painted by a very talented artist, 
Richard Wyatt, who deserves all the credit he can get. 
</P>
<P>
 WES CHRISTENSEN 
</P>
<P>
 Los Angeles  
</P>
