LIBERTY AND JUSTICE FOR ALL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 We of the Otavalan community, the Centro Cultural MUYUY and the Community of 
Quichua Art and Culture (CACUQ) thank writer Jonathan Kandell for his interest 
and goodwill ("Shuttle Capitalism," Nov. 14). However, as the inheritants of a 
historical process of self-determination of our peoples, we find the article 
limited.For example, take a deeper look at our socioeconomic work and our 
political work, with our single focus being the struggle for the fundamental 
rights of all humanity: liberty and self-determination. 
</P>
