<TEXT>
<P>
 "Whether we're selling tools or serving as a movie backdrop, it's all 
business." 
</P>
<P>
 -- David Gayman, president of Monrovia's Old Town Merchant's Assn., on filming 
in the city. His Valley Hardware Store was featured as a Western wear shop in 
