</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By HEIDI SIEGMUND 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 * * * A Tribe Called Quest, "Midnight Marauders," Jive. "Marauders" gets under 
your skin as if by osmosis, as rappers Q-Tip and Phife Dog lull you into their 
cool world with laid-back rhyme flows and even more languid beats.In an era 
when gats are becoming as trendy an accessory as beepers, ending one song with 
the pager operator's voice saying, "You're not any less of a man if you don't 
pull the trigger" shows that this Tribe clearly marches to its own beat. 
</P>
<P>
 New albums are rated on a scale of one star (poor), two stars (fair), three 
stars (good) and four stars (excellent). HEIDI SIEGMUND 
</P>
