<P>
 * * Angie and Debbie, "Angie and Debbie," Capitol. It's no surprise that 
Whitney Houston is the duo's chief supporter.Siblings of the gospel-singing 
Winans clan, Angie and Debbie have a vocal timbre and polish that recall 
Houston herself. She even puts in an appearance on "Light of Love," which is 
like most of the tracks here -- pretty but far from passionate. 
</P>
