</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
105TH TOURNAMENT OF ROSES; TROPHY WINNERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The 20 float winners of the 105th Tournament of Roses, with the theme 
"Fantastic Adventure." 
</P>
<P>
 1. Sweepstakes Trophy: Florists Transworld Delivery Assn. 
</P>
<P>
 2. Lathrop K. Leishman Trophy: Torrance 
</P>
<P>
 3. President's Trophy: Arco 
</P>
