<DOCNO> LA010294-0235 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 000441 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
January 2, 1994, Sunday, Valley Edition 
</P>
