N.Y. Giants 2 26 0 Houston 6 132 1 New Orleans 2 32 0 Atlanta 6 62 0 Detroit 4 
32 0 San Francisco 3 42 0 Atlanta 3 53 0 Washington 3 32 0 San Francisco 5 90 1 
