<P>
YERMAN TO ATTEND NEVADA 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By PAIGE A. LEECH 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Moorpark College offensive tackle Paul Yerman has given an oral commitment to 
play football at Nevada next season. 
</P>
<P>
 Yerman, a 6-foot-6, 270-pounder from Thousand Oaks High, also took recruiting 
trips to Syracuse and Pacific, and canceled a trip to Memphis State. 
</P>
<P>
 "Basically, I just liked Nevada more," Yerman said. "I felt like there was a 
lot of tradition there and I was impressed with the coaches and the program." 
PAIGE A. LEECH 
