<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
January 2, 1994, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Business; Part D; Page 6; Column 2; Financial Desk 
