 A photograph featured in "Will Palestinians Give Peace a Chance?" (by Kim 
Murphy, Dec. 5) that was identified as a demonstration by anti-Arafat militants 
was actually of a protest by right-wing Israeli settlers against Israel's peace 
agreement with the PLO.  
